data.title: Great Eye Care & Eye Doctor in Eyemart Express of Florence!
data.meta_description: Looking for an eye doctor near you in Florence? Look no further than Eyes over Florence, located inside Eyemart Express. We help with all your eye care needs!
data.text:
Caring Eye Doctors in Florence, South Carolina - Eyes Over Florence

At Eyes Over Florence, our skilled eye doctor is proud to provide for all your family’s eye care needs. Located inside Eyemart Express, on David McLeod Blvd, we provide a full-service eye care experience, from contact lens eye exams and fittings to eye exams for your DMV application, and eye emergencies! You can get your comprehensive eye exam with our caring eye doctors in Florence, South Carolina and eyeglasses with Eyemart Express , and most glasses are completed within the hour!

Eye Exams

Learn about eye exams offered by our Florence optometrist, what’s involved in a comprehensive exam & special considerations for kids and contacts.

Advanced Technology

We use the most up-to-date technology to ensure the best eye care possible. Learn about the tests we perform as part of an eye exam at Eyes Over Florence.

Contact Lenses

Our staff will help you find the best fit for your specific needs and explain how different lenses will impact your vision.

2 years ago

- Pat B.

Looking for an Optometrist Near You in Florence, SC?

Our optometrist takes the time to explain the results of your eye exam, describe your options and listen to your eye care needs.

Because maintaining good eye health is an ongoing partnership, we encourage you to ask questions and share your health information, which could be vital to monitoring, diagnosing and treating potential vision problems.

We accept a wide range of insurance plans to help you cover your eye care costs.

Eye Emergencies

If you have an eye emergency in Florence, SC don’t hesitate. Call us today. Our eye doctors have the latest technology and experience with foreign objects in the eye, eye infections, scratched eyes, painful or stinging eyes and other eye emergencies.

Please call our office at: 843-474-6443 for further instructions. We take most medical insurance plans.

Visit our eye emergencies page for more information.
